DEPENDENCIES
============

Packages that are part of standard Linux distributions and can be installed 
with the package manager of the distribution

0. gcc-c++ (version 4.8 or higher)
1. Boost 
[2. Armadrillo ]
[3. ZeroMQ (Version 3 or higher)]
4. NLopt 

Must be compiled at VM set-up

4. ZeroMQ C++ API to be cloned from https://github.com/zeromq/zmqpp
5. Theron (makefiles on how to build library - statically)
6. LA-Framework (a make must be made on the files in this directory)

LAUNCH
======

8. The meta-solver generates two files
      Variables.model
      Constraints.model

9. 'make LASolver' is done in LA-Reasoner directory

11. Start the self-standing program with two IP addresses
     [ LASolver <IP this machine> <IP metrics collector> ]
     LASolver
      

